<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//6a2f/6a2fe54a86ed8098dd8a61c41eb79cf0.com/large/18f9000c1049d58da679"> 
<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//f82a/f82a20ab695af714aee571ec07dbd084.com/large/18f9000c104a1e411fb8"> 
<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//950a/950a3d98c5d220ca4dd241901569ae18.com/large/18f7000c0c351bf55228"> 
<p>既然是妹妹把哥哥惹生气了，那妈妈聪明的先从引导妹妹发现问题开始，妹妹自己找到了讲和的解决办法。</p> 
<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//b369/b3691c7f815672d8a9c98e0dfbe30b63.com/large/183c000e25b9024b0e0f"> 
<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//9713/97137984ba41f83f833335b41931a109.com/large/183c000e25baca60144c"> 
<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//6575/6575725a7926cc76278ea5fb9eba0372.com/large/1839000d43772572bc26"> 
<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//d4d8/d4d8711451069a7895f0dcbb4e0c387f.com/large/183c000e25bc83f55b2e"> 
<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//19d6/19d66a404aa0b8e8ec0a4458d7d0a8a2.com/large/18f9000c104b548ff913"> 
<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//7827/7827fe18b4c62fbdf4470b44b03b7682.com/large/1835000d4295baf80c9f"> 
<p>但这并没有解决哥哥的疑惑，想要和平相处真得很难，尤其当别人伤害了我们的时候。</p> 
<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//8c3d/8c3d96e377fc49d9323bf63d962f0a31.com/large/1835000d42969b070895"> 
<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//dd4f/dd4fed3bbf1f6289f0da1e533028b36b.com/large/18f7000c0c36e5d58e3e"> 
<p>这个时候哥哥会问：所以我们不得不讲和？</p> 
<p>你猜妈妈怎么回答？</p> 
<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//2614/2614dd77f07c71dfec4ee15daaf7f761.com/large/18f7000c0c38a74bbf0d"> 
<p>什么是讲和？讲和是最好的办法？</p> 
<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//6597/659758597a76c22a5b82e94e7272d9d2.com/large/18f7000c0c39c4954cd5"> 
<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//57c2/57c204093e36b760f87aeadf6edd87aa.com/large/18f60001dd26aca9b8a9"> 
<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//6e96/6e96f51ac3e2223ce1530f3f16669424.com/large/18f9000c105033d486da"> 
<p>你有没有感受到，</p> 
<p>当孩子问一个问题后，</p> 
<p>父母适时的引导，</p> 
<p>会引发出孩子自己的思考，</p> 
<p>和更多问题。</p> 
<p>对，这就是家庭教养的真正力量。</p> 
<p>还有，我确实是要把这本好书推荐给每一个父母。</p> 
<p>但不是今天，是明天，哈哈……</p> 
<p>今天，等你先回答我的问题。</p> 
<p>明天我再来公布答案。</p> 
<p>做父母，别敷衍，认真点。</p> 
